Apps
Conference
Groups
IVR
Voice Mail

Class 5> Apps
Click + > Edit> Name the Application
Enter the Destination Number
Drag & Drop the IVR box
Select the IVR File that you wish to play. If you want to use your custom file you need to upload the file under File Section 
in .wav format
Select the invalid File
Select the Terminators key you wish to use
Select/ Enter the Result Variable, Example: Dtmf
Now drag the Condition from the side menu
Select/Enter the operand 1, example: variable_sip_refer_to
Enter the operand 2, example 2
Drag & Drop the ScriptForge from the side bar
Select the Scriptforge which was created
Drag & Drop the TTS box
Enter the Relevant text & click Save
